author: Kurzgesagt – In a Nutshell
description:
Our first PC game Star Birds is now available in Early Access on Steam! 🚀
We’ve spent over two and a half years working on this with the amazing team at Toukana Interactive, and we’re incredibly proud to finally share it with you.
Join your flock of Star Birds on a mission across the great beyond, establish a thriving mining operation, and discover new technologies to advance even further.
Play it now on Steam: https://kgs.link/sb-ealaunch

Thanks for all your support so far!
This wouldn't have been possible without you! 💖🦆
